parameters:
Orca Asparagus: I feel terrible for what I've done to you
all and the citizens... If I can be forgiven, I intend to
change my ways and make amends. Ever since I lost that time,
I've had an awakening...

Memimi: Don't worry about it, everything starts from now...
It's natural for people to have their say, but depending on
what you do from here on out, there's always a chance to
make things right.

Orca Asparagus: You're an amazing person... Because of me,
you ended up appearing in an adult video, and that
scandalous footage spread all over town... That's a bit hard
to undo... it's already...
Memimi: Could you not bring that up so much, please...

Brachiocondor: Hey, you seem to be doing quite well, Boss!
All the monsters that come here are buzzing about you. If
you ever have any trouble, remember you can always consult
us old-timers, okay?

Memimi: Hehe, don't push yourself too hard, Brachiocondor...
You guys must be busy with your duties at the city hall,
right? I hear you're working non-stop for the betterment of
Dorietoku City's public functions.

Brachiocondor: Don't underestimate our stamina... We train
differently than the younger folks! Besides, adults get
their energy from hanging out and having a few drinks
together like this...

Memimi: Speaking of which, you've been having drinking
parties every night... Even though you became a civil
servant, you're running a bar as a side job, aren't you?

Drillmaid: Thank you, Duke Shark... Ever since Orca
Asparagus and Shark Broccoli had their falling out, it's
been tough... I'm so happy we can all be together again...

Memimi: You've had it rough too, Drillmaid... From now on,
for the sake of Dirt City, please support Orca Asparagus. As
a fellow female monster, I'd like you to be there for
consultation as well...

Shark Broccoli: Grand Duke Shark, since you've taken over as
the big boss, it seems you're doing even better than my
time. The rumors have reached the city hall... I'm truly
glad to have met you... I'm a fortunate man...

Memimi: Shark Broccoli-sama, you're too kind...! It's
because you and the others laid the groundwork that we're
able to make such great strides now. I still have much to
learn...

Brachiocondor: No, no, your work has been impressive! We've
distanced ourselves a bit from the dark organization and are
working hard on municipal reform at the city hall, but
thanks to you guys rounding up the delinquents, we've been
greatly helped.

Drillmaid: All of us, personally, have been saved by you.
You should be proud... You're an amazing person, Drill
Drill...

Orca Asparagus: That... I'm sorry, looking back now, I
realize I was out of line... I've made up with Brother Shark
Broccoli... Thank you for letting someone like me who caused
such trouble join your ranks...

Memimi: Don't worry about it, if you're a brother of Shark
Broccoli-sama, then you're like family to me. I'm not so
narrow-minded as to reject someone who wants to atone and
start over... We can never have too many hands on deck.

Shark Broccoli: Grand Duke Shark... after you graduate from
Doritoku Academy, what will you do? If you're willing to
help me, I'll keep a post open for you as a civil servant...

Memimi: Thank you, Shark Broccoli-sama. After I graduate
from the academy... I plan not to join the city hall but to
study politics. I've come to want to fight on a bigger
stage, not just for Doritoku City.

Memimi: It's in my nature as a monster... If it's come to
this, I'll aim for the top! I'm thinking of trying my best
to become Prime Minister! I will do my utmost to ensure that
not a single boy or girl in this world has to feel sad
anymore!!

Shark Broccoli: So the time has finally come for you to
leave my side and stand on your own... If it's Grand Duke
Shark, I'm sure you'll make it happen... I'm looking forward
to it. It's about time for me to chase my own dream of
finding a cute girlfriend...
Memimi: Yes, that would be nice... a girlfriend...
